<BaseLayout title="404 - Page Not Found">
  <div class="page">
    <h1>404 — The road goes ever on, but not here</h1>
    <p class="quote">
      "It's a dangerous business, Frodo, going out your door. You step onto
      the road, and if you don't keep your feet, there's no knowing where you
      might be swept off to."
    </p>
    <pre class="ring">{gandalf}</pre>
    <p>
      It seems you've wandered into the Misty Mountains without a map.
      This page doesn't exist — perhaps a wizard moved it, or perhaps it
      was never meant to be found.
    </p>
    <p>
      Not all those who wander are lost — but you might be. Let's get you
      back to the Shire.
    </p>
    <div>
      <a href="/" class="button inline">
        <span class="button__text">Back to the Shire →</span>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .page {
    max-width: 760px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .ring {
    color: var(--accent);
    text-align: center;
    line-height: 1.1;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    border: none;
    background: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 1.5em auto;
    overflow: visible;
  }

  .quote {
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--comment);
  }
</style>
